
Running the Application
==========================

1) Import the project In J2EE version of eclipse (Imprt as java project not as maven project)

2) go to WebConect folder and than login folder, right click the login.xhtml and choose the option
   run on the server in run as menu
   Note: You need Apache tomcat web application server. In J2EE version of eclipse it is pre installed
   
3) you need Hive and Hadoop on the backend in order to run the use case
	-Hive can be accessed simply through HIVE JDBC API 
	-go to the ConnectionManager class in org.bsanalytics.apis.loaddate package and change
	 the JDBC url to your Hive JDBC url
	